children.name: Examples:
children.characters: Product Areas - Generate a Feedback Summary

children.name: Text
children.characters:
When customers select the option to generate a feedback summary from a set of feedback requests associated with a product area, we found that the usual spinning circle loading animation wasn't enough to hold their attention.

The generation process can take an average of 8 seconds but sometimes up to 20 seconds. To address this, we introduced a new animation that changes the perception of the time taken for creation. This engaging animation, accompanied by informative elements, interactive features, and microinteractions, ensures a more captivating and user-friendly experience.

We have implemented an animated loader that visually narrates the process of AI-driven generation from a selection of feedback requests to a concise feedback summary. This captivating animation lasts approximately 8 seconds, aligning with the average generation time. By utilizing this engaging visual representation, customers can follow the journey of their feedback transforming into a concise summary.
